title: Diner Dash: Flo on the Go
description:
Diner Dash: Flo on the Go is a trial version game only available for Windows, that belongs to the category PC games and has been created by Reflexive.

It's available for users with the operating system Windows 98 and previous versions, and it is only available in English. The program version information is not available and the latest update happened on 12/14/2006.

Since the game joined our selection of programs and apps in 2006, it has already achieved 131.658 installations, and last week it gained 52 downloads.

Diner Dash: Flo on the Go is a light game that requires less space than most programs in the section PC games. It's a game frequently downloaded in some countries such as United States, Indonesia, and Malaysia
